Welcome to the installation of Vostok Linux Workstation — an independent 
distribution focused on stability and simplicity.\n\n
This system is completely free, transparent, and open source. 
The installation process is intuitive. If you encounter any difficulties, 
please visit our resources or refer to the documentation.\n\n
${BOLD}https://vostoklinux.org${RESET}\n\n" 14 70

while true; do
    menu
done

exit 0
